  "description": "The gills catching light at the water surface. Morph at 1.0 — full sawtooth, all harmonics shimmering. Wide detune creates PPG-style chorus shimmer. LFO2 at 0.15 Hz: active enough to perceive as gentle ripple, not drift. BLOOM macro adds morph depth; DRIFT macro activates the full shimmer spread.",
